caption.p: Proportion of arbovirus monoinfections and co-infections, by virus type and year, compared with total number of infections registered in the Red Cooperativa para el Estudio de las Infecciones Importadas por Viajeros e Inmigrantes (+Redivi, http:// www.redivi.es) network, Spain, 2009–2018. A) Numbers of arbovirus infections; B) proportion of arbovirus infections compared with total number of infections registered.
